                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for nasf &amp;lt;fan.yong@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/beb1a5ce-52d0-11e2-9d36-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/beb1a5ce-52d0-11e2-9d36-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The client log shows that the client was evicted by OST, then cause related write cannot be replayed.&lt;/p&gt;

